  <sect3 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Gnome Robots</title>

    <para>
      <application>gnome-robots</application> is a classic 
      robots game where you have to avoid a hoard of robots 
      who are trying to kill you. 
    </para>

    &lfs76_checked;

    <bridgehead renderas="sect4">Package Information</bridgehead>
    <itemizedlist spacing="compact">
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Download (HTTP): <ulink url="&gnome-robots-download-http;"/>
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Download (FTP): <ulink url="&gnome-robots-download-ftp;"/>
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Download MD5 sum: &gnome-robots-md5sum;
        </para>
